replies.body:
Surprised no one mentioned Bard, lmfao.


Anyone have tips against Kalista? I feel like she's the biggest issue I've ever dealt with playing Bard. ;_;

That or Thresh.

{{champion:74}} 
His turrets hurt.
If I'm playing a ranged champ, usually AP mage, I'm squishy and my range isn't quite far enough to safely get rid of the turrets from a distance and thus I'm in range and taking damage while trying to get rid of them.
If I find a Donger up in top, as a melee is all I can do is to play passive and wait until mid game?

{{champion:89}} 
Consistent and easy stun, immobilize, and slow make me QQ on top of tanky and good burst
